      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1103-1137",
      "markText": "你须把受委屈当作生活，而从委屈中咂摸出一点甜味来，好使你还肯活下去。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1103&rangeEnd=1137",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1103&rangeEnd=1137"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_107_4945-4965",
      "chapterUid": 107,
      "range": "4945-4965",
      "markText": "小羊圈里，槐树叶儿拂拂地在摇曳，起风了。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=107&rangeStart=4945&rangeEnd=4965",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=107&rangeStart=4945&rangeEnd=4965"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_29_10710-10746",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "10710-10746",
      "markText": "对比他地位高的人，他把人家的屁也看成暗示；对比他低下的人，暗示便等于屁。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=10710&rangeEnd=10746",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=10710&rangeEnd=10746"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_71_10102-10177",
      "chapterUid": 71,
      "range": "10102-10177",
      "markText": "他一直奔了前门去，在西交民巷兑了支票，然后到车站买了一张二等的天津车票。“在天津先玩几天，然后到南京去卖卖草药也好！在北平恐怕吃不住了！”他对自己说。",
      "totalCount": 117,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=71&rangeStart=10102&rangeEnd=10177",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=71&rangeStart=10102&rangeEnd=10177"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_4_995-1031",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "995-1031",
      "markText": "在这年月而要安心写百万字的长篇，简直有点不知好歹。算了吧，不再说什么了！",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=995&rangeEnd=1031",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=995&rangeEnd=1031"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_65_11772-11835",
      "chapterUid": 65,
      "range": "11772-11835",
      "markText": "很快的，他想起一辈子的事情；很快的，他忘了一切。漂，漂，漂，他将漂到大海里去，自由，清凉，干净，快乐，而且洗净了他胸前的红字。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=65&rangeStart=11772&rangeEnd=11835",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=65&rangeStart=11772&rangeEnd=11835"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_3_1586-1631",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1586-1631",
      "markText": "一个民族的兴衰存亡，不仅在于其拥有发达的经济、先进的武器，而且取决于该民族普遍的社会心态。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1586&rangeEnd=1631",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1586&rangeEnd=1631"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_7_2035-2091",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2035-2091",
      "markText": "屋子都住满了自家的人，老者的心里也就充满了欢喜。他像一株老树，在院里生满了枝条，每一条枝上的花叶都是由他生出去的",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2035&rangeEnd=2091",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2035&rangeEnd=2091"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_21_2269-2306",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "2269-2306",
      "markText": "小崔很爱他的太太，只是在喝多了酒的时候才管辖不住他的拳头，而砸在她的身上。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2269&rangeEnd=2306",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2269&rangeEnd=2306"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_13_4329-4382",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "4329-4382",
      "markText": "他从神父的脸上看到人类的恶根性——崇拜胜利（不管是用什么恶劣的手段取得的胜利），而对失败者加以轻视及污蔑。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4329&rangeEnd=4382",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4329&rangeEnd=4382"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_16_1452-1508",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "1452-1508",
      "markText": "人类最大的惨剧便是彼此以武力估计价值，像熊或狗似的老想试试自己的力气，而忽略了智慧才是最有价值的，与真有价值的。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1452&rangeEnd=1508",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1452&rangeEnd=1508"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_58_2270-2295",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "2270-2295",
      "markText": "他有学问，而没有常识。他有脑子与身体，而没有人格。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=2270&rangeEnd=2295",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=2270&rangeEnd=2295"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_95_5320-5350",
      "chapterUid": 95,
      "range": "5320-5350",
      "markText": "瑞全没言语。他猛的用双手卡住她的脖子，她一声没哼，就断了气。",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=95&rangeStart=5320&rangeEnd=5350",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=95&rangeStart=5320&rangeEnd=5350"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_97_5728-5808",
      "chapterUid": 97,
      "range": "5728-5808",
      "markText": "头年的萝卜空了心，还能在顶上抽出新鲜的绿叶儿；窖藏的白菜干了，还能拱出嫩黄的菜芽儿。连相貌不扬的蒜头，还会蹿出碧绿的苗儿呢。样样东西都会烂，样样东西也都会转化。",
      "totalCount": 77,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=97&rangeStart=5728&rangeEnd=5808",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=97&rangeStart=5728&rangeEnd=5808"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_97_760-850",
      "chapterUid": 97,
      "range": "760-850",
      "markText": "他总是害怕，非常害怕。啃着啃着指甲，他会尖声大叫起来，一头钻到床上，拿被子把头蒙起来，能一憋多半天，大气也不敢出，捂得浑身大汗淋漓。他不敢掀被子，觉得死神就站在被窝外头，等着他呢。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=97&rangeStart=760&rangeEnd=850",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=97&rangeStart=760&rangeEnd=850"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_98_5368-5420",
      "chapterUid": 98,
      "range": "5368-5420",
      "markText": "又过了三天，李四爷还是人事不醒。末了，他睁开眼，看了看老伴，看了看家里的人，慢慢闭上眼，从此不再睁开了。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=98&rangeStart=5368&rangeEnd=5420",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=98&rangeStart=5368&rangeEnd=5420"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_5_1173-1203",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1173-1203",
      "markText": "一点也不像二孙媳妇那样把头发烫得烂鸡窝似的，看着心里就闹得慌",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26078968&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1173&rangeEnd=1203",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/32232710718deef8322406a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1173&rangeEnd=1203"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26078968_30_4507-4538",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "4507-4538",
      "markText": "而瑞丰这样的人偏偏会把这样的发脾气解释成有本事的人都脾气不好。",
